Files
-----
MIMS_ep2012_48.pdf 	- Paper describing the algorithm and its intended use.
data/cotfits.out   	- Fits to the cot function, produced by the algorithm.
html/index.html    	- Documentation for the class
main.cpp           	- example of how to use the class
main_createfits.cpp 	- program used to create data/cotfits.out
AntisymmetricExpFit.h   - header file for the fitting class
AntisymmetricExpFit.cpp - source file for the fitting class

* This code uses the Eigen library available at http://eigen.tuxfamily.org/

* Thanks to the CICADA research group at the department of Mathematics at Manchester University for funding this research.
